OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,FITV News' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew takes part in a quantum brain
OL,8,Fscan which uses revolutionary new
OL,9,Ftechnology that could help detect the
OL,10,Fearly signs of life-changing conditions
OL,12,FI'm sealed inside a white cubic room,
OL,13,Fshielded from magnetic fields outside.
OL,14,FOn my head is what looks like a bike
OL,15,Fhelmet connected by dozens of wires to
OL,16,Fa microchip-filled backpack. It's a
OL,17,Fquantum powered scanner which
OL,18,Fscientists say can help detect the
OL,19,Fearly signs of conditions like
OL,20,Fepilepsy, dementia and MS.
