OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,FIt's been developed at the University
OL,7,Fof Nottingham. It was there 50 years
OL,8,Fago Sir Peter Mansfield invented
OL,9,FMagnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI). That
OL,10,Fhas become a mainstay of medical
OL,11,Fscanning. This is different.
OL,13,F"MRI is exceptional technology," Matt
OL,14,FBrookes, Professor of Physics at
OL,15,FNottingham told me. "It can make
OL,16,Fstructural images of your brain with
OL,17,Fmillimeter precision but what it can't
OL,18,Fdo is measure the electrical activity
OL,19,Fin your brain. And that's what our new
OL,20,Fpiece of kit does."
