OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,FHow it works
OL,8,FThe OPM-MEG system uses quantum
OL,9,Ftechnology to monitor the electrical
OL,10,Fsignals passed around the brain.
OL,11,FInside each sensor is a gas of atoms
OL,12,Fwhose magnetic properties have been
OL,13,Faltered by a laser. Magnetic fields
OL,14,Ffrom our brain's activity changes how
OL,15,Fthe atoms move and by measuring that
OL,16,Fscientists can monitor brain activity.
