OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,FThe benefit of the new technology is
OL,7,Fthat it's lightweight, cheaper and you
OL,8,Fcan move while wearing it. In one test
OL,9,FI'm asked to turn on the spot.
OL,10,FScientists monitor my brain activity
OL,11,Fin real-time. If I had early
OL,12,FParkinsons they would be able to
OL,13,Fdetect signs of disease from my neural
OL,14,Fresponses.
OL,16,FIn another test, I hold two fingers
OL,17,Fonto braille sensors which tingle when
OL,18,Factivated. The data is then analysed
OL,19,Fby Dr Karen Mullinger and her team.
