OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,F"As the stimulus came on, the signal
OL,7,Freduces," she told me while pointing
OL,8,Fout fluctuations in brain activity on
OL,9,Fa graph.
OL,11,F"As the vibration on your finger
OL,12,Fstopped then we get this massive jump
OL,13,Fback up. What we see in patients with
OL,14,Fdifferent neurological diseases is
OL,15,Fdifferences in this response."
OL,17,FHad I suffered a concussion the line
OL,18,Fwouldn't peak as high. In MS sufferers
OL,19,Fit recovers at a shallower gradient.
