OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,FPrivate companies are already using an
OL,7,Folder and much more expensive version
OL,8,Fto offer patients brain MOTs. The
OL,9,Fgovernment, which has invested heavily
OL,10,Fin quantum technology, hopes to bring
OL,11,Fthis kit to the NHS within a decade.
OL,13,FRoger Mckinlay, who heads up quantum
OL,14,Ftechnologies for UKRI, said: "It's not
OL,15,Fsomething you might just find in a
OL,16,Fhospital but you might find it in your
OL,17,FGP's surgery. In the future as a low-
OL,18,Fcost way of initially diagnosing these
OL,19,Fconditions and catching them early."
