OL,3,CHow new brain scanning technology
OL,4,Ccould help detect conditions early
OL,6,FThe machines are being sold through
OL,7,FCerca Magnetics, a spin-out company
OL,8,Ffrom the university. So far eight have
OL,9,Fbeen shipped to top research centres
OL,10,Faround the world. As the technology
OL,11,Fcontinues to get cheaper and smaller
OL,12,Fit's hoped it will be rolled out to
OL,13,Ffrontline patient diagnostics soon.
